10:45.011 --> 10:46.713 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

10:46.813 --> 10:48.615 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
CHUCK SCHUMER (D-NY), Minority Leader: The
nominee for the secretary of education is

10:48.715 --> 10:55.622 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
one of the worst nominees that has ever been
brought before this body for a Cabinet position.

10:55.722 --> 11:00.827 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
On the grounds of competence, on the grounds
of ideology and on the grounds of conflicts

11:00.927 --> 11:02.462 align:left position:87.5%,start line:93.33% size:12.5%
of interest, she scores very, very low.

11:02.562 --> 11:04.297 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

11:04.397 --> 11:06.299 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
LAMAR ALEXANDER (R), Tennessee: There will
