11:11.671 --> 11:14.541 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
States Department of Education headed by Betsy
DeVos.

11:14.641 --> 11:19.612 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
We will be swapping a national school board
for what she believes in, which is a local

11:19.712 --> 11:21.114 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
school board.

11:21.214 --> 11:23.816 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The confirmation vote on DeVos
