11:23.917 --> 11:29.556 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
It could end in a tie, leaving Vice PresidentPence to cast the deciding vote.

11:29.656 --> 11:34.360 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
Congressional Republicans are also moving
to rescind more Obama-era regulations.

11:34.460 --> 11:39.699 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
The House voted today to abolish a rule on
cutting methane emissions from natural gas

11:39.799 --> 11:41.568 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
drilling.

11:41.668 --> 11:45.805 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
And the Senate gave final approval to dropping
a mandate that energy firms disclose what

11:45.905 --> 11:48.308 align:left position:75%,start line:93.33% size:25%
they pay governments for drilling rights.

11:48.408 --> 11:52.545 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
We are going to look at the drive to rollback rules later in the program.

11:52.645 --> 11:56.849 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
Enrollments on the national Obamacare Website have fallen slightly.

11:56.950 --> 12:01.821 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
